Cell["\<\
We take for simplicity from now on m2=1. Moreover, we go to the MUM point of \
the Calabi-Yau geometries which is a z=1/s.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.963143446688043*^9, 3.9631434724939117`*^9}, {
  3.963282225888897*^9, 3.963282228886836*^9}, {3.977313722915604*^9, 
