Cell["\<\
Here we see that it is not a total derivative and we get indeed a new third \
kind period.
We compare this now with the differential equation for the G-function found \
during the canonicalization.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.982310155944055*^9, 3.982310176822997*^9}, {
